If you believe that all men want is delicious meals and sex, then think again, otherwise you won t find your soulmate till death. Check out the things most men expect from their future wives.Yes, men crave to be understood. They want their future wives to support them during the difficult times, not blame for all their mistakes and failures. They want their wives to understand their habits and hobbies. We often lack understanding at work. Our parents and friends refuse to understand us too, which is why we are trying to find a spouse who will always support us regardless of the situation.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;